WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:02.411
<i>Previously on Z Nation...</i>

00:02.600 --> 00:05.331
Made it myself.
I call it the Z-Wacker.

00:05.520 --> 00:07.568
Well, slap my ass
and call me Sally!

00:07.720 --> 00:09.165
If it ain't Sketchy McClain.

00:11.640 --> 00:14.484
She's not Cassandra.
Not anymore.

00:14.640 --> 00:16.404
(SCREAMS)

00:16.560 --> 00:17.971
That didn't sound good.

00:18.160 --> 00:21.243
(SCREAMS)

00:23.600 --> 00:26.171
- MURPHY: Where's Cassandra?
-10K: I mercied her.

00:26.320 --> 00:30.086
I gave her life. And you had
no right to take that away.

